      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sound example of the high-revving S54 platform. It features essential subframe reinforcement and documented Vanos bulletproofing, addressing the primary longitudinal stress and internal timing concerns of the chassis. The 3.2L inline-six utilizes six individual throttle bodies for immediate throttle response, paired with a tactile 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable differential lock. Suspension kinematics remain sharp with refreshed bushings, providing the communicative steering and balanced turn-in typical of this iconic generation. A driver-focused specimen with a comprehensive service history and honest cosmetic wear.",
