    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that perfectly balances performance and comfort. This car has been my reliable daily driver and has been kept in a smoke-free environment. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though you will find the expected minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, superficial scratch near the rear wheel well\u2014nothing that detracts from its overall impressive curb appeal. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the leather seats remain supple with only minor creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and all electronic components, including the infotainment system and dual-zone climate control, function flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is sound. It has followed a strict service schedule with full synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles. Recent maintenance includes a fresh set of brake pads and a tire rotation, with the tread still showing plenty of life for several seasons to come. The engine runs smoothly without any odd noises, and the transmission shifts crisply through every gear. This is a turnkey vehicle ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately without the need for any upcoming major repairs.",
      "price": 34500.0,
