      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left for its next owner! Whether you\u2019re commuting to work or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car handles like a dream and has been super reliable for me. It's been well-loved and is totally ready to hit the road with you today. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you're going to love how it drives!",
      "price": 32500.0,
